ingredients.alim_nom_eng: Salt, white (sea, igneous or rock), iodine added, no other enrichment

ingredients_text: wheat flour 45,8%, glucose-fructose syrup, sugar, humectants (glycerin), dextrose, palm oil, strawberry puree 4,1%, skimmed milk powder, strawberry puree concentrate 1,4% (equivalent to 8,8% strawberries), acidifier (citric acid, malic acid), gelling agent (pectin), black juice concentrate , acidity regulators (sodium citrates, calcium citrates), salt, flavor, emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), mineral (iron diphosphate), may contain hazelnuts,
